Package org.validator.servlets

All Servlets of the application are saved within this package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cleanup
    Servlet to cleanup stale entries from the results catalog.
    FileHandler
    Servlet to handle the first step of the validation process, the loading of the XLSX file.
    ValidatorService
    This service sets up the ValidatorEngine and the ResultPublisher.
